INSERT INTO `blog_content` VALUES (166677,'Model shares jaw-dropping transformation photos','model-shares-jaw-dropping-transformation-photos','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"Check out man\'s jaw-dropping transformation who is now a hot model (Photos)\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"https://alexis.lindaikejisblog.com/photos/shares/5c9b407a3f261.jpg\" style=\"border:0px solid black; height:467px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; width:350px\" vspace=\"0\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>American model,<strong> Jodell Beckham Jr</strong>, has taken to his Twitter page to show off his jaw-dropping transformation including sharing an inspiring story of how he overcame depression and anxiety to become a hot model for top brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://alexis.lindaikejisblog.com/photos/shares/5c9b40ace60cf.jpg\" style=\"height:599px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharing before and after photos of himself, he wrote: <em>&#39;Feb/March 2017 I remember heading into the gym for the first time at 142kg with my depression crippling me and my anxiety stopping me from going to the weight section.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Now being flown out to model gym clothing as my job. Only God. Walk by faith, not by sight.&#39;</em><br />\r\n&rlm;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://alexis.lindaikejisblog.com/photos/shares/5c9b40d6b5da2.PNG\" style=\"height:601px; width:575px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n',13,1,12127,26,NULL,NULL,'2019-03-27 10:44:34','2019','3',' Jodell Beckham Jr,depression,anxiety ',NULL,'2019-03-27 10:24:35','2019-03-27 21:27:27',1,1,NULL),(166678,'Hearing-impaired student remanded in prison for sodomizing his classmate','hearing-impaired-student-remanded-in-prison-for-sodomizing-his-classmate','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://alexis.lindaikejisblog.com/photos/shares/5c9b414fc7651.jpg\" style=\"height:222px; width:333px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A student of the&nbsp;School for the Deaf in Kuje, Abuja, Sani Filo, has been remanded in Keffi prison, for sodomizing one of his classmates, Muhammed Kanum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Minister of Education, Adamu Adamu, disclosed this yesterday March 26th while&nbsp;presenting&nbsp;a committee report on the sexual abuse at the School for the Deaf in Kuje, Abuja.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The mother of the victim had peitioned the Minister&#39;s office in January this year after her son informed her of what Sani did to him.&nbsp; Upon receiving the petition, the&nbsp;Minister constituted a committee of inquiry. The committee presented its report yesterday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The report indicated that Sani had been prosecuted in a court and is currently being remanded in Keffi prison, Nasarawa state.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',9,1,1491,7,NULL,NULL,'2019-03-27 10:47:11','2019','3','Abuja secondary school,school for the deaf Abuja,Abuja,Minister of Education Adamu Adamu',NULL,'2019-03-27 10:25:57','2019-03-27 21:26:37',1,1,NULL),(166679,'Chaos at Dunamis church as traders revolt after their goods were burnt down','chaos-at-dunamis-church-as-traders-revolt-after-their-goods-were-burnt-down-2','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://alexis.lindaikejisblog.com/photos/shares/5c9b427cde07b.PNG\" style=\"height:409px; width:340px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was chaos at Dunnamis Church in Abuja as traders who conduct business around the church&#39;s surroundings arrived early in the morning to find their wares have been burnt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the protesting traders, they were warned a day before that their goods would be burnt if they did not move.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;They told us yesterday say them go burn am,&quot; one trader said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;This is wickedness in the highest order,&quot; another said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As they revolted, security forces stood around and tried to prevent them from getting into the church to register their displeasure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch the