yle=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">My name is Pastor Victor Stephen, Head, Central Admin of Dunamis Int&rsquo;l Gospel Centre.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Our attention has been drawn to a video clip circulating the cyber space concerning Traders&rsquo; properties being burnt down by Dunamis Church at the New Headquarters.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">We wish to state, though with dismay, that the Church, Dunamis was not responsible for that kind of act and can never be. Dunamis is geared towards the restoration of human lives and destinies and can never be associated with such heinous acts to indigent persons.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:0.0001pt; margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; margin-top:0in; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:norm